<div id="skill_sim_ability_Swordman1_tooltip" style="display: none;"><b>Bash: Enhance</b><br/><b>Type:</b> Passive<br/><b>Max Level:</b> 100<br/><br/>Increases the damage dealt on an enemy with [Bash] by 1% per attribute level.<br/><br/><b>Swordsman 1st Circle required</b></div><div id="skill_sim_ability_Swordman16_tooltip" style="display: none;"><b>Bash: Specialty</b><br/><b>Type:</b> Passive<br/><b>Max Level:</b> 3<br/><br/>Increases the damage dealt with [Bash] by 28 per attribute level.<br/><br/><b>Swordsman 3rd Circle required</b></div><div id="skill_sim_ability_Swordman2_tooltip" style="display: none;"><b>Thrust: Enhance</b><br/><b>Type:</b> Passive<br/><b>Max Level:</b> 100<br/><br/>Increases the damage dealt on an enemy with [Thrust] by 1% per attribute level.<br/><br/><b>Swordsman 1st Circle required</b></div><div id="skill_sim_ability_Swordman13_tooltip" style="display: none;"><b>Gung Ho: Enhance</b><br/><b>Type:</b> Passive<br/><b>Max Level:</b> 50<br/><br/>Amplifies the physical damage increase effect and the decreased defense effect of [Gung Ho] by 1 per attribute level.<br/><br/><b>Lv3 Gung Ho required</b></div><div id="skill_sim_ability_Swordman14_tooltip" style="display: none;"><b>Concentrate: Enhance</b><br/><b>Type:</b> Passive<br/><b>Max Level:</b> 50<br/><br/>Increases the additional damage of [Concentrate] by 2 per attribute level.<br/><br/><b>Lv3 Concentrate required</b></div><div id="skill_sim_ability_Swordman25_tooltip" style="display: none;"><b>Pommel Beat: Enhance</b><br/><b>Type:</b> Passive<br/><b>Max Level:</b> 100<br/><br/>Increases the damage dealt on an enemy with [Pommel Beat] by 1% per attribute level.<br/><br/><b>Swordsman 2nd Circle required</b></div><div id="skill_sim_ability_Swordman27_tooltip" style="display: none;"><b>Double Slash: Enhance</b><br/><b>Type:</b> Passive<br/><b>Max Level:</b> 100<br/><br/>Increases the damage dealt on an enemy with [Double Slash] by 1% per attribute level.<br/><br/><b>Swordsman 3rd Circle require